Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_msix_pba1

The MSI-X pending bit array cannot be burst read.

PF_PND is assigned to PCIe related errors. The error bit can only be found in PBA1 when SLI_PKT_MAC()_PF()_RINFO[TRS]=63 (i.e. 64 total DPI Packet Rings configured).

This register is accessible by the PF. A read by a particular PF only returns its own pending status. That is, any PF can read this register, but the hardware ensures that the PF only sees its own status.
